<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[soak 100 g sultana in water (cold) for 15 m; drain ]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[boil 500 g cauliflower in water (salted) on high heat until al dente, about  4m; chill   in water (cold) ]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[chop (thinly) 200 g onion; stir fry   in oil (olive) on medium heat until wilted, about  4m ]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add and fry 100 g pine nuts until browned, about  2m ]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[cut (chunks) the cooked cauliflower; add to the pine nuts and fry for 20s ]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add 30 g achovies / blue cheese ]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[soak a pinch of saffron in 1 tbsp of cauliflower water; add to the sauce and cook  for 20s ]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add water as needed  as sauce cooks on low heat until pasta ready ]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[cook 500 g bucatini / spaghetti, thick / maccheroni in cauliflower water on high heat until al dente, about  10m ]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[toast 50 g bread crumbs ]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add over   cooked pasta and sauce]]></step>
&gt;</directions>
